# GitNexus MCP Kit — repositories to index (OPTIONAL)
# ------------------------------------------------------------
# You usually DON'T need to touch this file. By default the kit
# AUTO-DETECTS every repo in your workspace and indexes it.
#
# Use this file only if you prefer to pin repos explicitly, or to
# add repos that live OUTSIDE the workspace. Entries here are merged
# with auto-detected repos (set GITNEXUS_AUTO=0 to use ONLY this list).
#
# One repo path per line. Absolute, or relative to this kit folder.
# Lines starting with #, and blank lines, are ignored.
# ------------------------------------------------------------

# --- Examples (uncomment / edit) ---
# /Users/you/Downloads/apps/scanapp/parametereditor
# /Users/you/work/pathologysuite/worklist-service
# ../my-sibling-repo
